line_1: Her Conquest ore the Flow'rs proclaims.
line_2: She sits and flow'ry Wreaths she frames;

line_1: To flocks and rocks, to hills and rills proclaims,
line_2: His oaten reed to rural ditties frames,
Plenty and Health attend his beams,
Shall bid AUGUSTA rise in Flames;

line_1: Have they again (as Sacred Song proclaims)
